		</div><!--/.story-photo-->
		
		<div class="cat-icon science"><a href="http://news.harvard.edu/gazette/section/science-n-health/">View all posts in Science &amp; Health</a></div>
		<div class="story-info">
		  <div class="header">Next:</div>
			<h3><a href="http://news.harvard.edu/gazette/story/2013/08/getting-around-gluten/"  onclick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent','next','title','http://news.harvard.edu/gazette/story/2013/08/getting-around-gluten/']);">Getting around gluten</a></h3>
			<div class="date">
			<span class="byline">By Valerie Vande Panne, Harvard Correspondent <span class="divider">|</span> </span>August 9, 2013
			</div>

		</div><!--/.story-info-->
